<section xml:id="images-verifying-install"
    xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
    xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="5.0">            
            <title>Verifying the Image Service Installation</title>
    <para>You can ensure that your Image service is running by using
        the glance CLI with an authorization token:</para>        
    <literallayout class="monospaced">glance -A e660589d-76a7-42ee-bd52-dbd456af0745 index</literallayout>
    <para>In return you should see a listing of images (if you have
        uploaded any). Here's an example.</para>
    <literallayout class="monospaced">
ID               Name                           Disk Format          Container Format     Size          
---------------- ------------------------------ -------------------- -------------------- --------------
6                tty-kernel                     aki                  aki                         4404752
    </literallayout>
    <para>You can find the version of the installation by using the
        glance --version command:</para>
            <literallayout class="monospaced">glance --version</literallayout>
        
        <para>The version number 2011.3 corresponds with the Diablo
        release.</para>
    
    <literallayout class="monospaced">glance 2011.3</literallayout>
    </section>
